features.name: Better Foliage
features.description: Better Foliage is a mod that will make your Minecraft worlds more impressive, mainly by improving how vegetation looks.

features.name: Sound Filters
features.description: If Sound Physics isn't working properly, Sound Filters can provide a lower quality spatial sound. Better than nothing, but worse than Sound Physics.

features.name: Smooth Water
features.description: Enables ambient occlusion in water blocks.

features.name: Blur
features.description: Adds a Gaussian blur under GUIs. May affect performance.

features.name: Chunk Animator
features.description: Adds transition animations when loading chunks.

features.name: Optifine
features.description: Upgrade your graphics and improve game performance with Optifine.

features.name: Ambient Sounds
features.description: Add realism and depth to Minecraft with new ambient sounds.

features.name: Dynamic Lights
features.description: If you do not want to install Optifine, enable this mod for visibility in dark places.

features.name: Inventory Tweaks
features.description:
Sort your inventory with ease using Inventory Tweaks.
Quark has a built in inventory sorter, but you may use Inventory Tweaks instead if you prefer it.

features.name: Sound Physics
features.description: Adds spatial surround sound to Minecraft.

features.name: ItemPhysic Lite
features.description: Enhance dropped items in the world.

features.name: Real First Person Render
features.description: See your body and arms when looking down in first person mode.

features.name: Borderless Windowed Mode
features.description:
Enable support for borderless windowed mode instead of exclusive fullscreen mode.
Allows for faster alt-tabbing,  but may lower overall performance.

features.name: Dynamic Surroundings
features.description: Enhance Minecraft with new sounds and visual effects.
